# Data Dictionary — wu2019_teams

## Data source
Web of Science + Microsoft Academic Graph + USPTO + GitHub — Citation + authorship network
Access: public-substitute; Provenance: SciSciNet local

## Key variables
- Unit of analysis: team-paper
- Time window: 1954-2000s
- Sample N: 30000000
- Filter rules: complete citation data, team-size deciles

## Indicator definitions
- Formula: CD = (Ni - Nj)/(Ni + Nj + Nk)
- Parameters: team-size deciles, D-index by decile
- Computation steps: build citation network, compute CD per paper, group by team size
